high_descs: Turn left and go to the black trash can
Pick up the tomato from the trash can
Turn around and go to the refrigerator
Place the tomato in the refrigerator between the lettuce and tomato and close the door. Open the door and take out the tomato
Turn right and go to the microwave above the sink on the left
Open the door, put the tomato in the microwave and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward to the refrigerator, then turn around and face the garbage can on the floor.
Pick up the tomato from the garbage can.
Cool the tomato in the refrigerator, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink, then turn left towards the microwave above the stove top.
Put the tomato in the microwave and close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black garbage that's in front of you and turn right to face it.
Pick up the tomato that's in front of you in the garbage.
Turn right and take a step then turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the stove that's on your left then turn left to face it.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato in the microwave.
